    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Also at 1st level, your cursed energy is able to be molded into various effects, known as Cursed Techniques.</p><p> Unless stated otherwise, when a Cursed Technique would require you to make an attack or force a creature to make a save, you use your highest relevant attack or DC between your Ninjutsu, Taijutsu, and Genjutsu attack and Save DC.</p><p> You may use one cursed technique on a turn.</p><p> You have as many techniques as displayed in the class table.</p><p> You may switch out one technique for another on a rest.</p><p></p>",
